Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't hurry, my child will die, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... heard them... talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are going to... burn the entire city... tomorrow night...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turkish town... they are going to burn it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell them quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else my town...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will burn my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:04.22,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,183)\pos(357,317)}Wolf's Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rug in the antique shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its existence is meaningless unless someone knows \N its value, someone like myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to look at adults like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I end up making a lot of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not gonna get you anything good to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be sorry if you tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never team up with a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.  Don't cry.  Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom will be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That baby doesn't have a mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hang around here by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home to your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a mom either?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it is nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are waiting for that Tenma person to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the same as that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did his mom go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was taken by some bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place is very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, an Asian person was trying to assist me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he was struck by a car right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Asian man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you said that Tenma person was Japanese, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go!  Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man... man from the extreme right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After work, I left the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I forgot the scarf, so I went back to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man... was talking on the phone with friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to tell the townspeople...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I... was caught... and locked here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boy... still small...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cannot run if the fire starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Göderich asked me to deliver some fruit to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Wolf will be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person who was in the picture with my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the one who has the most knowledge about Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The professor said that he may know Johan even \N better than his little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you cannot die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Excellency Wolf will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will see my meritorious deed in capturing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is "His Excellency" to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the firs to realize Johan's talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is like a dream come true to hear \N words of praise from General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have assembled the crew for the \N Turkish district burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any changes to the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my dinner as I watch the bright red sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why my fun filled dinner will be \N ruined if the timing is even slightly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell them they will be punished if they can't \N carry it out according to the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan, won't command you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is impossible... to make Johan sit \N at the top of your organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... doesn't have the cheap racial discrimination \N or prejudices... like you people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan mocks the entire human race!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a rare kind of customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give this customer my usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is gonna grow up rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they drink that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma's jacket...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get you out of that room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't do anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll sneak out of here and notify your \N people in town about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What street should I go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calvin Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calvin Street.  Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boy will be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll help get you out of here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is your... name...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I arrived in Germany... only \N bad things happen to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I meet a nice person...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are... friends, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is your boy's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:08:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that man Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who captured him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is "His Excellency" Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is waiting somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are taking this man with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this was my achievement...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I would kill him after I showed \N him to "His Excellency" myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he came looking for that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That child has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let him go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this filthy child to "His Excellency" Wolf's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dispose of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he is so noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he is an annoyance, kill him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That was my subordinate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive our rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an important guest of General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell them quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else my town...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will burn my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are... friends, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right, Ayse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Göderich...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is... dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will soon arrive at the mansion \N where General Wolf is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nina there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please be rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is an important guest, like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Turkish woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know anything besides what we were told.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go back to town!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calvin is gonna be burned down right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't tell the townspeople...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the lady that treated me to dinner and the baby will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it is our responsibility to take you to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get to the Turkish district by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a man, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go, everyone on Calvin Street will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can hitch a ride, it will take you about thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being so rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please start the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for doing this to you after you \N trusted me enough to return my gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you didn't seem like you would \N stop if I had not done it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:14:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning that a gun is not merely an accessory to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm sure General Wolf will be quite pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is in this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will first meet with General wolf \N and Professor Göderich.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, show me that she is safe first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Göderich is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only Göderich...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but all of his subordinates were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have disposed of the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time we brought General Wolf to this mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she had already disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Dr. Tenma, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably won't recognize me when you see my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You appear completely different compared \N to the picture from ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is due to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you go faster, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have got to be kidding!  I'm already pushing 200KPH!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200KPH?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your meters are broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People's names are mysterious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...know that my name is Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I join a group of strangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I must tell them that my name is Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the proof that I am Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the first one to find out \N about Johan, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, twelve years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you sent him to Kinderheim 511 in Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to become an East German vanguard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you tried to raise him to be a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a man of talent to support a country \N on the verge of collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you chose him as a new Hitler...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and are trying to expand a fascist organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I am merely involved with this \N organization as a matter of convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the others are trying \N to fashion him into Hitler...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that is just a foolish plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with a man like Hitler, it went that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It if had been Johan..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who gave him the name "Johan."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We took the two siblings in when we found them \N wandering near the Czechoslovakian border.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two had evaded the heavy security near the border...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and were on the verge of death due \N to malnutrition and exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fell unconscious soon after we picked them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same as when you saved his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he regained consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I asked him a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How do you feel right now?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he answered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You'll know soon enough."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any evidence that I am Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people I've known have left \N this world, one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife, my child...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my parents, my siblings, my relatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my subordinates, and my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all died, one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was Johan's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that can verify that I am Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the large sum of money I took with \N me when I escaped from East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from my own belief that I am myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...nobody knows who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You will know soon enough."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what he meant when he said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll be waiting for you at the ruins of the \N Hilden & Engles warehouse in Romberg"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan was here this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he killed Göderich and his subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now another man who knows me is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina probably went there after seeing this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry and tell the people on Calvin Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I'm blessed with good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the fire to make that rug mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it so loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let anyone hear about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just the people in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think what would happen if the fascists overheard us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would never make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially with those skinheads with the swastika tattoos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a Turkish woman held in this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That women was found dead on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman was the only person Johan didn't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the work of one of Professor \N Göderich's subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that man can kill Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he might still make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...?
